reviews.review_text:
This show is THE BOMB !!!!! So like it is the best for waking up my 18 year old son and 15 year old daughter for school, since their alarm clocks seem to keep failing.  I start out the show at regular volume, and then max out for the drums.  Yessir, if that dont raise the Dead, nuthin will.  Even my neighbors thank me.

Thanks for the fab parenting aid.
